headline.print_headline: Somali Militants Stone Woman to Death
headline.main: Somali Militants Stone Woman to Death

lead_paragraph: Somali al Shabaab militants stoned a woman to death in the southern town of Barawe on Friday after a court they had set up declared her guilty of adultery, the militants and witnesses said.
